{
  "stem": "12053.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They published an article in their press in the [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Harwich ?] newspaper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then I got letters because-- from sailors who remembered us, from an old lady who was a teacher then who came to teach us English, lived across the road in Dover Court, wonderful letters.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And one letter I got with a-- the most famous of all the photographs, of a policeman holding two little children on-- one on either hand.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she told me that was her father, the policeman who had recently died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She sent me that photograph, and that started the ball rolling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't know how it happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Like topsy, it growed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It became worldwide.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I found a friend, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Paula ?] Hill, who is, you know, who is very clever girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She's an archivist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And she actually became-- she wasn't an archivist to start with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She became an archivist through this business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And she researched, and she found dozens of wonderful photographs in what was the former that is [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Houten ?] Deutsche Company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They've got all these pictures that were taken when we arrived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I've got quite a few in here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But now I've lent them to the Watford Theatre Company only yesterday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They're going to exhibit it with the play that's coming on in May.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it started the ball rolling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it rolled, and it rolled, and never stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we started-- we got the Jewish yearbook.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My husband then was very helpful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Must say, for a whole year, he was very pleased to help me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We organized a reunion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I realized within a couple of weeks that the synagogue wouldn't have been big enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I started to research and learn in the I never knew 10,000 children were given permission to enter.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
